<h1>Find parallel flow directions</h1>

<p>
This tool can be used to find cells in a stream network grid that possess parallel flow directions based on an input <a href="FlowPointerD8.html"><i><b>D8 flow-pointer</i></b></a> grid. Since streams rarely flow in parallel for significant distances, these areas are likely errors resulting from the biased assignment of flow direction based on the D8 method.</p>
<p>The output raster is of the <i>integer</i> data type and <i>Boolean</i> data scale.</p>


